://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/72664/', '', 'Asenapine, Pimavanserin, Lumateperone, Iloperidone, Amisulpride, Droperidol, Cariprazine, Brexpiprazole, Paliperidone, Lurasidone', 'Mometasone, Mometasone furoate, Beclomethasone dipropionate, Cromoglicic acid, Ciclesonide, Mometasone furoate, Flunisolide, Cromoglicic acid, Betamethasone, Nedocromil, Beclomethasone dipropionate', 1767369485);
